{"tid":1254513,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想買1.5匹分體冷氣機 連安裝費8k 係咪被人呃","createTime":"2019-06-24T07:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T11:02:46.000Z","uid":117232,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ccae9e967f17d18d67cf61e402c005df33e43dea","tid":1254513,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"最近屋企冷氣壞左<br />\n老豆話識買冷氣連安裝有discount,<br />\n話屋企無窗台所以安裝費會貴少少<br />\n利申 唔知咩牌子，但聽到8k up真係呆左。<br />\n<a href=\"http://見price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A6%8Bprice.com&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=9301bed9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">見price.com</a> 1.5 日立分體都好似5.5k左右。<br />\n<br />\n老豆平時買咩都高過市價同唔實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27ba46cbe4d08c13ecdb1995929e2fd0f3478e0","tid":1254513,"uid":53672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"無窗台要裝架係貴d 你幾樓?"},{"pid":"a69f21ca27d614fd728bb60e126867a0500ad211","tid":1254513,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:17:50.000Z","msg":"有無窗台或者預位先"},{"pid":"29119923e732f20de0b6f2d0c63af12b49506ecc","tid":1254513,"uid":259400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"要搭棚架喎"},{"pid":"b74f4e8dcab0d247185737f071548ab00e81b266","tid":1254513,"uid":65391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"最近新屋裝咗一部1.5 同2匹變頻冷氣<br />\n4K + 8k 拉喉裝鋁架要4千幾<br />\n我裝潢緊所以有棚 如果你另要搭棚 8千都合理"},{"pid":"1fc838b48c1a7806f773bc8832c955a574ac506d","tid":1254513,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛搭棚"},{"pid":"4b0714da88efa3f13f0765946b6bd1f5a5d3d872","tid":1254513,"uid":99008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:20:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfe5c50d0e472a87115e1127b2e24cb8e28ecbe9","tid":1254513,"uid"